title: Historic Iowa 511 Traveler Information Events
description: CSV files of events in the Iowa 511 feed starting in 2013, organized by month and year.?Includes all events found on the?Iowa 511?website, except for winter road conditions.

title: Historic 511 Iowa Road Conditions
description: Iowa Winter Road Conditions. Conditions have been archived every 30 minutes during the winter season (October 15 to April 15). Data archived by Iowa DOT GIS team on behalf of the Office of Traffic Operations. Current archived winter seasons are 2015-2016 and 2016-2017.

title: AVL Historic Pings
description: This layer contains all Iowa DOT vehicles that are traveling more than 5 MPH during the winter season organized by year and month. Data goes back to January 2013.
